Furukawa-sensei is VERY knowledgeable on her subject.  According to Ide-sensei, more Japn-education experience than any of the other first-year teachers, and she definitely knows enough to be teaching the higher level classes as well.  I learned a lot from this class.
Furukawa sensei was excellent, especially for a first year teacher. Very energetic and helpful, class was very fun to go to.
